1.  The prevous url from which the request to present route has come is stored in :
        req.headers.referer
        
In this version (v3) following changes are made:
    1. user, post and comment models are modified.
    2. team routes and team views are created
    3. group routes and group views are created
    4. "add user(by username) to group" route is created: user/:user_id/goups/:goup_id/user
    5. Create "Leave Group" functionality
    6. Create "Leave Team" functionality